{"tid":1987132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以香港現況，\"Stay Home\"唔係\"Save Lives\"而是\"Kill Economy\"","createTime":"2020-04-24T09:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T04:11:26.000Z","uid":166360,"like":6,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d87c9ef5ee30866db29f722ef6483ce5c4c37fd5","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"當初確診數字開始上升時，很多人話&quot;Stay Home，Save Lives&quot;，但近期新增個案跌至極低水平，本地個案幾乎是0。經濟因之前疫情及限制人群措施已受重大打擊。如果宜家依然Stay Home不外出消費，就唔係Save Lives而是Kill Economy。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不認同"},{"pid":"0912cd77e89028a690164f244614498bbfe406e9","tid":1987132,"uid":204539,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"Kill the Protest, Save the Government<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e82f44707a0632c7dc20b106826418ce22ea399","tid":1987132,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"Why not both?"},{"pid":"fe124076b33574f3675068cc30ca3b05baa7e3d1","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e82f44707a0632c7dc20b106826418ce22ea399","tid":1987132,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"Why not both?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"Save Lives又唔Kill Economy?<br />\n單靠網購無可能做到"},{"pid":"d39d5637081e297f5f32fde1f1b190cc64d38811","tid":1987132,"uid":28730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fe124076b33574f3675068cc30ca3b05baa7e3d1","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e82f44707a0632c7dc20b106826418ce22ea399","tid":1987132,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"Why not both?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":