/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabknxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=250b2575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a82252b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n&quot;現時本港大約有5%的患者需入住深切治療部，但當年沙士有四分一患者需深切治療部&quot;<br />\n&quot;現時很多仍然留院的病人都很精神，毋須利用儀器供氧，甚至可以在病房玩電話或做運動，只是等待病毒檢測呈陰性反應&quot;<br />\n&quot;病人失去味覺和嗅覺的情況都很短暫，亦只有少部分病人有肺部纖維化情況&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">都話左疫情被誇大啦</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9239d37b75942bdea9ca3200eb74d6dd8782d0a","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d39d5637081e297f5f32fde1f1b190cc64d38811","tid":1987132,"uid":28730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fe124076b33574f3675068cc30ca3b05baa7e3d1","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e82f44707a0632c7dc20b106826418ce22ea399","tid":1987132,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"Why not both?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"Save Lives又唔Kill Economy?<br />\n單靠網購無可能做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔：Why not kill economy? 我就係要攬炒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔怕攬炒，是否已經準備好食草過活呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抑或連登仔全部身家豐厚或有鐵飯碗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe77e79268031219c4a0d7be23a994183c3c01e","tid":1987132,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T11:08:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/139VIBa8dIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F139VIBa8dIE&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabknxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=ee83dc78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/139VIBa8dIE</a>"},{"pid":"d9bd57eff3f2287ad71f4807011b3b900c5a64b4","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"見到不少人周末都&quot;Hang Out. Support Economy&quot;<br />\n真係心感欣慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一周兩日零確診 周末外出人流增 市民怎看待 未來一年戴口罩疑問！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988780</a><br />\n<br />\n疫情稍緩銅鑼灣周末人頭湧湧 市民：出街抖吓氣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988768</a>"},{"pid":"5283ef7606a044372179d576bdfecb77d7aa8dae","tid":1987132,"uid":5889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"14-21日lagging variable 都可以比你講到咁樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f951b03b5cf5ff228c6be04555bd1eaf685272","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5283ef7606a044372179d576bdfecb77d7aa8dae","tid":1987132,"uid":5889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"14-21日lagging variable 都可以比你講到咁樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"對了<br />\n說好了的復活節長假病例大爆發呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還未計大多數病人潛伏期少於14日喎"},{"pid":"682c932dc83012b6731367bef6db9f58431e6d82","tid":1987132,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57f951b03b5cf5ff228c6be04555bd1eaf685272","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5283ef7606a044372179d576bdfecb77d7aa8dae","tid":1987132,"uid":5889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"14-21日lagging variable 都可以比你講到咁樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"對了<br />\n說好了的復活節長假病例大爆發呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還未計大多數病人潛伏期少於14日喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:22:22.000Z","msg":"Err on the safe side <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好過到最後出事，要啲醫護係前線搵命博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a365b5c5bf0b0a82e34da2ae63e82fcd8f827c","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"專家料2%病人痊愈後再驗出有病毒 勿將出院者視完全康復<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局昨日(25日)公布，本港目前最少有8名新冠肺炎出院病人出現「復陽」的情況，即患者康復出院後，對病毒檢測再次呈陽性。醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超推算，目前本港約有2%出院病人復陽，認為比率不算低，要小心處理，建議為所有出院病人再進行一次病毒檢測，了解有多少名病人復陽，以及找出高風險復陽人士。<br />\n<br />\n梁指，目前本港有逾700人出院，當中約有200人剛出院，未完成14天的醫學監察；已出院、並完成醫學監察的人士約有400至500人，當中有8人出現復陽情況，即復陽人士比率約2%，屬偏高水平。他建議，現階段勿將出院病人視作完全康復，因一部分人體內的病毒或仍未完全清除，建議為所有出院人士再作一次覆檢，避免有個案流入社區。<br />\n<br />\n梁又稱，目前復陽個案分為3類，包括出院後一段時間復陽、出院後有病徵，以及病毒維持一個月仍持續陽性。他解釋，人體的免疫系統會在發現病毒兩星期內產生很強的免疫反應，以消滅病毒，惟此病毒可能有辦法抑制免疫系統，令其在人體內持續逾一個月。他又不排除復陽個案是因為抽樣本的問題；或有病人的病毒量以極低程度複製，令病人身體出現狀況，才令病毒重新活躍。<br />\n<br />\n問及如患者出現抗體，是否代表不會再受感染，梁表示此病毒出現抗體與病毒消除的關係並不密切，最重要是要視乎血液抗體可否中和或抵抗病毒，以流感疫苗為例，接種疫苗的人仍會有感染風險，只是病徵會較輕微而已。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200426/bkn-20200426134414465-0426_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200426%2Fbkn-20200426134414465-0426_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabknxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=663f16d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200426/bkn-20200426134414465-0426_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde</a><br />\n<br />\n連登親病毒派: 嘩! 隻病毒好恐怖呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一於支持永續限制人群措施!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44955f2a3a66ccdb9176aa974aa442d1e4960393","tid":1987132,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9239d37b75942bdea9ca3200eb74d6dd8782d0a","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d39d5637081e297f5f32fde1f1b190cc64d38811","tid":1987132,"uid":28730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fe124076b33574f3675068cc30ca3b05baa7e3d1","tid":1987132,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"Save Lives又唔Kill Economy?<br />\n單靠網購無可能做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔：Why not kill economy? 我就係要攬炒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔怕攬炒，是否已經準備好食草過活呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抑或連登仔全部身家豐厚或有鐵飯碗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"一人一口政府班底咪算囉<br />\n反正咁多狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口裏說攪炒 然後又怕攪炒到自己<br />\n即係點"},{"pid":